22: NAME
23: kgb - .kgb files archiver
25: SYNOPSIS
26: kgb [-<m>] archive.kgb [filename  ...] [@files_listing @...]
28: kgb FILE.kgb
30: DESCRIPTION
31: kgb
is a file archiver with high-compression rates (and high CPU and memory cost).
33: OPTIONS
34: Compressing:
35: Set compression level (memory usage), values:

37: 1: 3 MB
38: 2: 6 MB
39: 3: 18 MB (default)

(best compression)

48: Filename of the new KGB archive. It must
not
exist, otherwise it will fail.
50: [filename
51: File or list of files to compress.
53: [@files_listing
54: File(s) containing a list of file names to be compressed, separated by a new line.
56: Uncompressing:
